hopobject.body: What's the interest rate on this account? generic norvasc 10mg July 2001 was not Mariah Carey's month. After busily promoting her soon-to-be-released flick 'Glitter,' the Grammy award-winning diva showed up to MTV's TRL acting O.D.D. After handing out popsicles, she began a bizarre striptease. 'I just want one day off when I can go swimming and eat ice cream and look at rainbows,' Carey told a bewildered Carson Daly. Days later, the pop star was hospitalized, citing 'extreme exhaustion.' Hey, we'd be tired too if we had to spend that much time trying to convince people 'Glitter' was good.
